（Rajeev Mittal）表示，中国年轻一代的养老储蓄率创新高令人鼓舞。相信未来第三支柱账户制的设立和税收优惠的推出，将进一步鼓励民众增加定期的养老储蓄，为他们下一步进行长期投资，夯实资金基础。报告：年轻一代储蓄率创3年来新高，月均储蓄1624元"},"attached_info":"Cj8Ir6zVz+DpkbRQEAMaCDcyMjgxMzM1IKCN6IsGMCE4pgZAMHIJNDk1MDAxNzEyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"50 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-5da038d200889844152d50c23b4e9a3f_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"49_1635472165.9275045","card_id":"Q_493944281","target":{"id":493944281,"title":"中国航天为什么在这两年密集发射？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/493944281","type":"question","created":1634899860,"answer_count":73,"follower_count":514,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[24600,33865,153138,153160,153442],"comment_count":11,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"这两年中国陆续发射嫦娥五号、天问一号和神舟十三号等航天器，取得骄人成果，中国航天为什么集中在这两年爆发呢？"},"attached_info":"Cj8Ir6zVz+DpkbRQEAMaCDcyMDQ2NzA0IJSvyosGMAs4ggRAMXIJNDkzOTQ0MjgxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"49 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-ac71d4b0afc4aa659affc6ef1d9ef36a_b.jpg"}]}],"description":{"time":"2021-10-29 09:49:26"}}